From: Joe Perches <joe@perches.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jun 2011 19:08:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] drivers/net: Remove casts of void *
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
